author: dildick
body:
#### PR description:

Basic infrastructure to pack and unpacker GEM clusters in the CSC packer/unpacker. Once the GEM-CSC is included in the TMB DAQ output data format, we can start filling in the blanks. The code does not do anything yet. There should be no changes in any of the workflows.

#### PR validation:

Tested with WF 27434.0

FYI @barvic
title: Basic infrastructure for GEMs in CSC packer/unpacker
